==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Membranous
<hw>Mem"bra*nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>membraneux</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Pertaining to, consisting
of, or resembling, membrane; <as>as, a <ex>membranous</ex> covering or
lining</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Membranaceous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Membranous croup</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>true
croup. See <er>Croup</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Memento</ent>⟦br⟧
